rows.label: tlk41400071_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I envy people like you, who can
travel the world so freely.

rows.label: tlk41400071_03_msg0002
rows.name:
I've been here for ten years
already. What's the difference
between you and me?

rows.label: tlk41400071_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Where we were born? Whether
we have a Blade? There's
nothing I can do about that.

rows.label: tlk41400071_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I must have just been unlucky.
I was born in the wrong era.
